**Synapses**:
- [[001_Introduction_To_Embedded|ARDUINO 001]] - Arduino basics
- [[003_PWM_And_Motors|ARDUINO 003]] - PWM output
- [[005_Communication_Protocols|ARDUINO 005]] - Serial protocol deep dive

